h1 You might be able to get legal aid
p
  ' Based on the answers you have given, you might be financially eligible for legal aid.
  ' But we don’t know yet whether your problem is covered.

form name="applicationForm" ng-submit="submit(applicationForm)"
  dl style="margin-bottom: 30px"
    dt
      = label_tag 'extra_notes', caption: 'In your own words, please tell us more about your problem (optional)'
    dd
      textarea.form-control(
        id="extra_notes"
        rows="7"
        class="m-full"
        ng-model="application[5].extra_notes"
      )

  h3 Next step
  p You’ll need to speak to an operator who can help you apply for legal aid. Please submit your details so that they call you back.

  fieldset
    dl ng-repeat="field in application"
      dt
        = label_tag '{{field.name}}', caption: '{{field.label}}'
        help-text field="field"
      dd
        input.form-control(
          id="{{field.name}}"
          type="{{field.type}}"
          class="m-{{field.size || 'normal'}}"
          ng-if="field.type == 'text'"
          ng-model="field.value"
          ng-required="{{!field.optional}}"
        )
        textarea.form-control(
          id="{{field.name}}"
          rows="{{field.rows || 4}}"
          class="m-{{field.size || 'normal'}}"
          ng-if="field.type == 'textarea'"
          ng-required="{{!field.optional}}"
        )

  .notice
    h4 What happens next
    p
      ' If the operator you speak to believes you can get legal aid,
      ' they will find you specialist legal help, like a phone call with a solicitor
      ' or support from a family mediation service.

  p.action: button.button Submit
